n style=\"font-size:inherit\"><span style=\"font-family:華康中圓體\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:inherit\">根據輪子愈多愈大就愈好推的法則，來選保證萬無一失，現在一般款式行李箱大多是可</span></span><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:inherit\">360</span></span><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:inherit\">度旋轉的四輪款式。但是在捷運、地鐵上，就要看好箱子以免上演追箱的戲碼。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<div style=\"border:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; margin-top:0px; padding:0px\"><span style=\"font-size:medium\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Arial,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;PingFang SC&quot;,&quot;Heiti SC&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,&quot;Source Han Sans&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-size:1em\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,&quot;Source Han Sans&quot;,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;PingFang SC&quot;,&quot;LiHei Pro&quot;,&quot;Heiti SC&quot;,Gotham,&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:#1a1a1a\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-size:inherit\"><span style=\"font-family:華康中圓體\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:inherit\">很常在路上看到許多人即使是4輪箱，也會用&quot;空姐拖法&quot;只用2輪在拖．這樣的拖法對輪子滿傷的，容易造成輪子前後不平衡，這樣就浪費4輪的功能。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></div>\n\n<div style=\"border:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; margin-top:0px; padding:0px\"><span style=\"font-size:medium\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Arial,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;PingFang SC&quot;,&quot;Heiti SC&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,&quot;Source Han Sans&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-size:1em\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,&quot;Source Han Sans&quot;,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;PingFang SC&quot;,&quot;LiHei Pro&quot;,&quot;Heiti SC&quot;,Gotham,&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:#1a1a1a\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-size:inherit\"><span style=\"font-family:華康中圓體\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:inherit\">所以好的4輪行李箱，只要把拉桿拉到舒服的高度，輕鬆推著走就好囉～</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"text-wrapper\" id=\"BJeA5NCxQ\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px; border:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; margin-top:0px; padding:32px; text-align:start\">\n<div class=\"entry\" style=\"border:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; margin-top:0px; padding:0px\">\n<h2 style=\"margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; text-align:left\"><span style=\"font-size:medium\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Arial,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;PingFang SC&quot;,&quot;Heiti SC&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,&quot;Source Han Sans&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-size:1em\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,&quot;Source Han Sans&quot;,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;PingFang SC&quot;,&quot;LiHei Pro&quot;,&quot;Heiti SC&quot;,Gotham,&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:#1a1a1a\"><span style=\"font-size:3em\"><span style=\"font-family:inherit\"><span style=\"color:#f1009b\"><span style=\"font-size:inherit\"><span style=\"font-family:華康中圓體\"><span style=\"font-size:26px\"><span style=\"font-family:inherit\">飛機輪：崎嶇地形也好推</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></h2>\n\n<div style=\"border:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; margin-top:0px; padding:0px\"><span style=\"font-size:medium\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Arial,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;PingFang SC&quot;,&quot;Heiti SC&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,&quot;Source Han Sans&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-size:1em\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,&quot;Source Han Sans&quot;,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;PingFang SC&quot;,&quot;LiHei Pro&quot;,&quot;Heiti SC&quot;,Gotham,&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:#1a1a1a\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-size:inherit\"><span style=\"font-family:華康中圓體\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:inherit\">很多人大推的飛機輪呢？小編個人推薦飛機輪，就算箱子本身不是飛機輪，也是加錢自己換飛機輪。為什麼呢？當你晚上九點發現你預定民宿歇業，流落在異國街頭在非常難移動的石板路，推著</span></span><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:inherit\">29</span></span><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:inherit\">吋的行李箱時，就知道為什麼要買飛機輪</span></span><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:inherit\">...(</span></span><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:inherit\">咳，離題</span></span><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:inherit\">)</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:inherit\">主要原因是飛機輪，實際上有</span></span><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:inherit\">8</span></span><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:inherit\">顆輪輪子，輪子尺寸也比較大。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></div>\n\n<div style=\"border:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; margin-top:0px; padding:0px\"><span style=\"font-size:medium\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Arial,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;PingFang SC&quot;,&quot;Heiti SC&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,&quot;Source Han Sans&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-size:1em\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,&quot;Source Han Sans&quot;,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;PingFang SC&quot;,&quot;LiHei Pro&quot;,&quot;Heiti SC&quot;,Gotham,&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:#1a1a1a\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-size:inherit\"><span style=\"font-family:華康中圓體\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:inherit\">當行李箱過重的時候，在非滑順平面的地面上推動時，就非常有感。例如，一樣重的箱子，飛機輪與大四輪，在地毯上面推，飛機輪很順暢，大四輪也許會因為箱子過重卡卡的。<br />\n若是有跑歐洲的朋友，尤其又要跑自助的。歐洲的石板路堪稱輪子殺手，多來個幾次，大四輪就死了。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></div>\n\n<div style=\"border:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; margin-top:0px; padding:0px\">&nbsp;</div>\n\n<div style=\"border:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; margin-top:0px; padding:0px\"><span style=\"font-size:medium\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Arial,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;PingFang SC&quot;,&quot;Heiti SC&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,&quot;Source Han Sans&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-size:1em\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,&quot;Source Han Sans&quot;,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;PingFang SC&quot;,&quot;LiHei Pro&quot;,&quot;Heiti SC&quot;,Gotham,&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:#1a1a1a\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-size:inherit\"><span style=\"font-family:華康中圓體\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:inherit\">不過也不是非飛機輪不買，如果只是一般旅遊，沒有一直推著箱子跑來跑去，行李箱尺寸材質顏色都很滿意，大四輪也很好的～</span></span><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:inherit\">在地毯上、石板路，兩輪因為依靠手部的力量反而暢行無阻～</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></div>\n\n<div style=\"border:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; margin-top:0px; padding:0px\">&nbsp;</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<p><a class=\"img-wrapper\" href=\"https://go.shopping.friday.tw/event/201806/201806-seo-luggage/index.html#\" id=\"BJlz2NAe7\" style=\"box-sizing:inherit; margin:0px; padding:400px 0px 0px; border:0px; font-style:normal; font-variant-ligatures:normal; font-variant-caps:normal; font-variant-numeric:inherit; font-variant-east-asian:inherit; font-weight:400; font-stretch:inherit; font-size:medium; line-height:inherit; font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Heiti SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans&quot;, sans-serif; vertical-align:baseline; display:block; width:950px; max-width:100%; position:relative; background:50% 50% / contain no-repeat #fff2f2; letter-spacing:normal; orphans:2; text-align:start; text-transform:none; white-space:normal; widows:2; word-spacing:0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width:0px\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://hiiir-fastdeliever.s3.amazonaws.com/_images/images/2018/SEO/luggage/5b2363acd0d2e7_13353639.jpg\" style=\"border:0px; bottom:0px; box-sizing:inherit; font:inherit; left:0px; margin:0px; padding:0px; position:absolute; right:0px; top:0px; vertical-align:baseline; width:950px\" /></a></p>\n\n<div class=\"theme theme-PD_0L4S_A\" id=\"111\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px; border:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; margin-top:0px; padding:0px; text-align:start\">\n<div class=